text: Shino Magariyama (born 20 September 1987) is a Japanese female water polo player. She participated at the 2014 Asian Games, 2015 World Aquatics Championships, 2017 World Aquatics Championships, and 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * Shino Magariyama -Asian Water Polo Championships 2012 - Day 2 zimbio Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese water polo players
